<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4551828>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 1. Map of collection locations (red diamonds) and approximate host plant ranges (shaded area) for the species included in this study (Little 1971, eFloras 2008): R. bushi infests Shepherdia argentea (A); R. tabellaria infests Cornus stolonifera (B); R. persimilis infests Prosartes hookeri (green) (C); R. electromorpha infests C.drummondii (green) C. racemosa (blue) and C.foemina (stricta) (light brown) (D). Individual map panels outlined in the same color as those associated with species in Fig. 4." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4551828/files/figure.png" .

